highlights.text: Saran has the most spots on Top Songs Thailand. “รออยู่อย่างนั้น” is the highest at #38.
“หากจะเพียงขอ (Sincare)” by PURPEECH has been on Top Songs Thailand the longest, at 205 weeks straight.
“PARADISE” by TREASURE is the highest new entry on Top Songs Thailand at #50.
“wanna be yours (อยากให้เธอรัก)” by Violette Wautier is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Thailand, up 83 spots at #24.
